 computing services rates page for more information getting started log in to sponsorship manager and the follow the online instructions for sponsoring a service last modified tue 2 aug 2011 at 15 35 pages about this service overview sponsored services sponsorship details actions sponsorhip manager find answers submit a helpsu request stanford answers related pages sunet id group imap authority manager email footer links stanford university helpsu user login stanford university terms of use copyright complaints
